1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,480
We begin as any student does —
with a name, and an ambition.

2
00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:09,483
The moment you enroll, aion-edu
mints you a cryptographic identity,

3
00:00:09,483 --> 00:00:11,424
a key that is yours alone.

4
00:00:11,424 --> 00:00:17,398
And it lays out your path: the exact
lessons, and the masters who'll teach them.

5
00:00:17,398 --> 00:00:20,006
Press begin, and class is in session.

6
00:00:20,006 --> 00:00:21,416
This is not a video.

7
00:00:21,416 --> 00:00:26,421
The professor reasons with you, in
their own voice — and then they ask.

8
00:00:26,421 --> 00:00:28,466
You answer in your own words.

9
00:00:28,466 --> 00:00:34,247
There are no multiple-choice shortcuts
here; mastery is something you demonstrate.

10
00:00:34,247 --> 00:00:38,510
When you've met every outcome,
the professor records mastery —

11
00:00:38,510 --> 00:00:40,366
and a credential is sealed.

12
00:00:40,366 --> 00:00:42,017
Signed by the professor.

13
00:00:42,017 --> 00:00:45,386
Bound to the very rubric
you were graded against.

14
00:00:45,386 --> 00:00:48,274
Untamperable from the moment it is struck.

15
00:00:48,274 --> 00:00:52,708
It lands in your transcript — a
wallet of everything you have proven.

16
00:00:52,708 --> 00:00:56,242
Each credential carries its
own proof, ready to travel.

17
00:00:56,242 --> 00:01:00,505
Hand it to another institution,
and watch what happens.

18
00:01:00,505 --> 00:01:05,930
Accepted — because they recognize
the university that vouched for you.

19
00:01:05,930 --> 00:01:07,790
And to one that doesn't?

20
00:01:07,790 --> 00:01:10,425
Rejected — instantly, and offline.

21
00:01:10,425 --> 00:01:11,976
The same credential.

22
00:01:11,976 --> 00:01:15,076
The trust turns entirely on recognition.

23
00:01:15,076 --> 00:01:20,166
Download the diploma, and you hold
the whole proof in a single file.

24
00:01:20,166 --> 00:01:26,079
Anyone — with nothing but this file and
a verifier — can confirm it is genuine.

25
00:01:26,079 --> 00:01:28,774
Change one grade, and it is refused.

26
00:01:28,774 --> 00:01:30,645
The seal cannot be faked.

27
00:01:30,645 --> 00:01:32,849
Behind it all is the federation,

28
00:01:32,849 --> 00:01:37,534
where institutions establish trust
as deliberately as they grant it.

29
00:01:37,534 --> 00:01:39,394
They recognize one another.

30
00:01:39,394 --> 00:01:43,734
They co-accredit joint degrees,
requiring signatures from both.

31
00:01:43,734 --> 00:01:47,179
They can delegate trust,
and they can withdraw it.

32
00:01:47,179 --> 00:01:51,726
And they can checkpoint the entire
state, signed, for any dispute.

33
00:01:51,726 --> 00:01:56,785
A university that teaches like
the greatest minds in history —

34
00:01:56,785 --> 00:01:59,560
and credentials like cryptography.

35
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,460
aion-edu.

36
00:02:00,460 --> 00:02:01,600
Sealed in proof.
